author: sergeyb
msg: [CXF-5144] Closing async Response objects when possible too

author: ggregory
msg: Change CSVFormat#Iterable<CSVRecord> parse(final Reader in) to return a CSVParser, which is compatible since CSVParser implements Iterable<CSVRecord>. This allows a caller to end the parsing by calling CSVParser#close() or to use CSVParser in a Java 7 try-with-resources, without tracking a reader or input stream.
